@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bxcteo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 * (wp.sin(v0 + 0.70) * (v1 + 0.14 - v1 + 0.24)))
    v0 = (wp.cos(v1) / tmp)
    v2 = 0.85
    tmp = (v0 + ((v0 + 0.68 - v0 + 0.08) + (tmp + 0.81 - v0 + 0.52)))
    v1 = wp.sin((0.85 - wp.exp(v1 + 0.09)))
    data[tid] = v0
